description.text: Tastefully updated, this Silicon Beach home is conveniently located near Marina restaurants, shops, Equinox gym, and just minutes away from Venice, Culver City, Playa Vista, and LAX. The bright and sunny residence offers 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, with a spacious private front and back yard that's perfect for entertaining. The entire home has been beautifully remodeled, giving it a fresh and modern feel. Gorgeous hardwood floors run throughout, complemented by custom light fixtures that add a unique touch. The kitchen boasts built-in stainless steel appliances and sleek architectural concrete countertops, while its open design seamlessly connects it to the dining and living room, creating an expansive and inviting atmosphere. The dining room features custom lighting and a large window, adding to the overall charm of the space. The bathroom offers a frameless glass enclosure for the bath/shower, beautifully tiled for an elegant look. Additionally, there is a garage with an attached studio/home office/gym/creative space, providing versatility for various needs, along with ample parking on the property. The home also includes a new central heating and air conditioning system, ensuring year-round comfort. The low maintenance landscape and energy-efficient features make this home easy to upkeep. All windows are double pane glass with shade window coverings, enhancing privacy and energy efficiency. This is not your typical leased home! All appliances are included, making it move-in ready. Situated on a quiet block in the heart of the desirable Silicon Beach neighborhoods, this location offers the best of both worlds. And with the beach just two miles away, you can enjoy the coastal lifestyle. A gardener is also included, ensuring the exterior remains well-maintained.

description.text: This lovely single-level Traditional home is gated and surrounded by privacy hedge and designed gardens creating a peaceful retreat. You will find a wow factor entry, with exceptional natural light filling the expansive living room overlooking the outdoor dining room. To the right is a dining room seating eight which opens to the remodeled galley kitchen with granite counters; a garden window and stainless-steel appliances open to a remodeled laundry room. The two auxiliary bedrooms overlook the front gardens and have double sinks with shower tub adjoining through one hall. The primary bedroom and adjoining expansive office has curved windows overlooking the back gardens and outdoor dining. The gardens include mature fruit trees and a lovely mixture of cactus and flowering plants. The property features a street to alley, with room for a swimmer's pool and outdoor water feature.

description.text: Welcome to your new luxurious living space! This stunning open studio floor plan is perfect for anyone seeking a city escape. It boasts an expansive walk-in closet, spacious bathroom, and a massive outdoor living space with panoramic views. Enjoy the abundant natural light and luxurious finishes. Step outside onto your private, generous deck and indulge in al fresco dining while basking in the sun. The outdoor living space offers approximately 442 sq ft of total privacy, making it perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing after a long day. The penthouse is designed with a modern kitchen featuring designer finishes and Frigidaire Gallery stainless steel appliances. This unit is pre-wired for DirectTV, internet, and telephone. A smart Nest thermostat and front-loading washer/dryer add to the convenience of the apartment. Located just minutes from the heart of Mar Vista, this exquisite penthouse offers a peaceful and sophisticated living environment that is sure to impress. Don't miss your opportunity to live in luxury. Contact us today to schedule a viewing! Covered parking is also included.

Available unfurnished ($6, 500/mo) and furnished ($7, 000/mo) is this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom property in one of LA's most desirable residential neighborhoods. Tucked away on a walkable, tree-lined street, this Tudor home offers spacious accommodations within its 1, 424 square feet, with a private driveway fit for two cars and an entire grass lawn to play in. Enjoy close proximity to Venice, Santa Monica, Culver City, and dozens of fantastic eateries and city attractions. Notes There is a detached 400-square-foot back house on the property that is currently occupied by one tenant. Furnished rentals will require a two-month security deposit. One-year minimum lease furnished or unfurnished.

This gorgeous & spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhome offers hardwood floors, an open living room with an adjacent dining area, & gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, custom cabinetry, a breakfast bar, & Bosch stainless steel appliances. The sun-filled second floor showcases the 3 ample sized bedrooms, including the primary suite with a custom walk-in closet & en-suite luxurious spa-like bathroom with a dual vanity & separate shower/soaking tub. This immaculate townhome also features HVAC, recessed lighting, in-unit laundry, & attached private 2-car garage. The fantastic location is w/ coveted Culver City services!

IDEAL FOR A SOBER LIVING FACILITY. 8 bedrooms / 7 bath house with separate entrances, with 2 full kitchens. Newly remodeled and fully furnished, including TV, internet, modern new furniture, plenty of closet space (furnished down to serving dishes, beddings, towels, etc). There are 6 parking spaces on the lot. Plenty of non-restricted parking in the street. One main house, which has a large kitchen, living room, dining area, 2.5 baths, 2 bedrooms each with its own private bath. Central air and one office. There are 6 extra-large studios, each with its own private entrance, bathroom, and a separate mini split system for AC and heat. One Studio has its own private patio. Another Studio has its own private balcony. 3 separate driveways. All with electronic gates. Very large back yard.
